      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing OEM bushings. Mechanically, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rod bearings have been addressed for preventative maintenance. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with deep luster, while the interior shows zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
